    { name: "Artificial Tears", type: "Ophthalmic lubricant", action: "Provides moisture and protection to the cornea when eyelid closure is impaired", sideEffects: "Temporary blurred vision", contra: "None significant", pearl: "Essential for eye protection in CN VII palsy where the patient cannot fully close the affected eye; use ointment at night with eye patch" }
